Description:
Automates scraping and downloading PDFs for EU Commission speeches/statements.

Runs for all commissioners.
Lets you specify the start date for automation with --start-date (DD-MM-YYYY).
Sends email notifications for new downloads.
Only processes items from the specified date.

How it differs from scraper.py:
scraper.py is manual: run for a single commissioner and date range.
auto_scraper_notify.py is automated: runs for all commissioners, logs downloads, sends notifications, and allows date control.
Usage:

Activate your Python environment.
Run: python auto_scraper_notify.py --start-date DD-MM-YYYY
Replace DD-MM-YYYY with your desired date.
Check your email for notifications.
Requirements:

Python 3.x
SMTP server configured for email notifications
All dependencies from requirements.txt



